      • getAverageSellPrice

        @MessageMapping(value="/averageOffer")
public void getAverageSellPrice()
        Gets the average daily price of the offers. Everytime a new offer is added, we update and broadcast to all clients All users, both buyers and sellers, must subscribe to this topic when a connection is opened
